T* (Generate code/UI from the prompt; do NOT rewrite or shorten the curriculum.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (---) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (## curriculum-export.json -- schema) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (```) Tj
T* ({) Tj
