T* (}) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Lesson = {) Tj
T* (  slug, title, tagline, estMinutes, xpReward, difficulty \(1-5\),) Tj
T* (  requiresMath?  \(slug of a math lesson this physics lesson depends on\),) Tj
