T* () Tj
T* (Build a gamified "digital university" called **Master Numerics** -- an immersive journey) Tj
T* (through mathematics and physics from kindergarten through graduate level. Curriculum is) Tj
T* (DATA \(imported from `curriculum-export.json`\), not hand-written pages. Two themed,) Tj
T* (Duolingo-style scrollable lesson-path worlds, a local in-browser answer-checking engine,) Tj
T* (embedded videos, downloadable worksheets, formula flashcards, and a restrained) Tj
T* (black-and-white + one electric-blue-accent design. Free-demo mode: ALL content is open,) Tj
T* (the store sells ONLY cosmetics, and nothing about learning is paywalled.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (### Design system \(strict\)) Tj
T* (- Monochrome base \(near-black bg `#06070B`, off-white text `#F4F6FB`\) + ONE accent:) Tj
