T* (              "title": "The big idea",) Tj
T* (              "content": {) Tj
T* (                "markdown": "Three facts you already know combine into the answer:\\n\\n1. The Moon makes no light -- it ) Tj
T* (only **bounces sunlight** \(last lesson!\).\\n2. So **one half** of the Moon is always lit -- the half facing the Sun.\\n3. ) Tj
