T* (                  "A force is a push or a pull -- it can start, stop, speed up, slow down, turn, or squash things.",) Tj
T* (                  "Bigger forces make bigger changes in motion.",) Tj
T* (                  "Heavier \(more massive\) objects need more force for the same change.",) Tj
T* (                  "Friction is a hidden force between rubbing surfaces that resists sliding -- and makes walking ) Tj
T* (possible.",) Tj
T* (                  "Forces come in pairs: push something and it pushes back on you.") Tj
