T* (              "content": {) Tj
T* (                "markdown": "Magnets are hiding all over your home. They pin art to the fridge, snap tablet covers shut,) Tj
T* ( hold cabinet doors closed, and spin inside every electric motor -- fans, blenders, electric toothbrushes, electric ) Tj
T* (cars.\\n\\nAnd magnets do something most forces can't: they **work without touching**. Every push or pull from the last ) Tj
T* (lesson needed contact -- foot on ball, hand on wagon. Magnets reach across empty space, just like gravity does. ) Tj
T* (\(Spoiler: planet Earth itself is a gigantic magnet, and that fact has guided sailors home for a thousand years.\)") Tj
