T* (carry oxygen tanks, why airplane cabins are pressurized, and why a sealed chip bag from the seaside puffs up like a ) Tj
T* (balloon in the mountains: the air **inside** the bag keeps its push, while the air outside pushes back less. Unbalanced ) Tj
T* (pressure always wins arguments.") Tj
