T* (                "intro": "Drag the Sun across the sky. Watch the light's path through the atmosphere stretch as the Sun ) Tj
T* (drops -- and watch the sky shift from noon blue to sunset fire as the blue gets scattered away.") Tj
T* (              }) Tj
T* (            },) Tj
