T* (      "slug": "low-earth-orbit",) Tj
T* (      "name": "Low Earth Orbit",) Tj
T* (      "subtitle": "Forces & Simple Machines",) Tj
T* (      "description": "Four hundred kilometers up, the Space Station circles the Earth every 90 minutes. In ) Tj
T* (near-weightlessness -- where friction nearly vanishes -- the true rules of force show themselves: pushes and pulls, ) Tj
T* (simple machines, work and power, and the energy that ties it all together.",) Tj
T* (      "gradeRange": "5-6",) Tj
