T* (                "headline": "The Fastest Thing There Is",) Tj
T* (                "sub": "Light crosses a room in a few billionths of a second and the gap from the Sun in eight minutes. ) Tj
T* (Bend it with a curved piece of glass and you can capture a galaxy.") Tj
T* (              }) Tj
