T* (                      "Energy rises with frequency \(and falls with wavelength\).",) Tj
T* (                      "Radio waves have very long wavelengths \(low frequency, low energy\).",) Tj
T* (                      "X-rays have very short wavelengths \(high frequency, high energy\).") Tj
T* (                    ],) Tj
T* (                    "answer": "X-rays carry far more energy -- which is exactly why X-rays can be hazardous and radio ) Tj
T* (waves are harmless to pass through.") Tj
T* (                  },) Tj
T* (                  {) Tj
