T* (                "markdown": "**Average velocity** is displacement per unit time:\\n\\n$$\\\\bar v = \\\\frac{\\\\Delta ) Tj
T* (x}{\\\\Delta t}$$\\n\\nIt is a vector -- its sign is the sign of the displacement. Units are metres per second, ) Tj
