T* (axes to align with the ramp, the acceleration has only **one** non-zero component \(along the slope\) and the ) Tj
T* (perpendicular direction is in equilibrium \($N = mg\\\\cos\\\\theta$\). Choosing smart coordinates to make a problem simple is) Tj
T* ( a theme that runs all the way up to Lagrangian mechanics.") Tj
