T* (                  "Impulse $\\\\vec J = \\\\vec F\\\\Delta t = \\\\Delta\\\\vec p$ \(impulse-momentum theorem\).",) Tj
T* (                  "Impulse is measured in $\\\\text{N*s} = \\\\text{kg*m/s}$.",) Tj
T* (                  "For a fixed $\\\\Delta p$, longer contact time means smaller force -- the airbag principle.") Tj
