T* (              "content": {) Tj
T* (                "simId": "collision",) Tj
T* (                "intro": "Choose 'Stick together', set the carts moving, and launch. Momentum before equals momentum ) Tj
T* (after -- but compare the speeds and you'll see kinetic energy has dropped.") Tj
T* (              }) Tj
T* (            },) Tj
T* (            {) Tj
