T* (                  "Moment of inertia $I$ is rotational mass; for a point mass $I = mr^2$.",) Tj
T* (                  "Mass farther from the axis contributes much more \($r^2$\).",) Tj
T* (                  "A hoop has larger $I$ than a disk of equal mass and radius.",) Tj
T* (                  "Newton's law for rotation: $\\\\tau_{net} = I\\\\alpha$.",) Tj
T* (                  "Parallel-axis theorem: $I = I_{cm} + Md^2$.") Tj
T* (                ],) Tj
