T* (                  {) Tj
T* (                    "title": "The skater spins up",) Tj
T* (                    "problem": "A skater spinning at $\\\\omega_i = 2\\\\,\\\\text{rad/s}$ with $I_i = 6\\\\,\\\\text{kg*m}^2$ ) Tj
T* (pulls in to $I_f = 2\\\\,\\\\text{kg*m}^2$. Find the new spin rate.",) Tj
T* (                    "steps": [) Tj
T* (                      "Conserve $L$: $I_i\\\\omega_i = I_f\\\\omega_f$.",) Tj
T* (                      "$6 \\\\times 2 = 2 \\\\times \\\\omega_f$, so $\\\\omega_f = 12/2$.",) Tj
T* (                      "$= 6\\\\,\\\\text{rad/s}$.") Tj
T* (                    ],) Tj
T* (                    "answer": "$\\\\omega_f = 6\\\\,\\\\text{rad/s}$ -- three times faster.") Tj
