T* (                  "Centripetal acceleration $a_c = v^2/r$ points to the center.",) Tj
T* (                  "Centripetal force $F_c = mv^2/r$ is whatever real force points inward.",) Tj
T* (                  "Period and speed are linked by $v = 2\\\\pi r/T$.",) Tj
T* (                  "There is no outward 'centrifugal' force in the inertial frame.") Tj
