T* ( positive charges and **toward** negative ones -- the direction a small positive test charge would be pushed.\\n\\nField ) Tj
T* (lines picture it: denser lines mean a stronger field. Between two parallel charged plates the field is **uniform** ) Tj
T* (\(constant strength and direction\), the configuration inside capacitors and the setup for accelerating particles in a ) Tj
