T* (              "title": "Deeper dive: spacetime",) Tj
T* (              "content": {) Tj
T* (                "markdown": "Relativity merges space and time into a single four-dimensional **spacetime**. Different ) Tj
T* (observers disagree about separate distances and times, but they all agree on one combined measure, the **spacetime ) Tj
T* (interval**. Events that are simultaneous for one observer are not for another -- simultaneity is relative. This ) Tj
T* (geometric view, perfected by Minkowski, is the launchpad for general relativity, where gravity becomes the curvature of ) Tj
T* (spacetime itself.") Tj
