T* (                "markdown": "Two particles can share a single wavefunction, so that measuring one instantly fixes the ) Tj
T* (state of the other, no matter how far apart -- **entanglement**, what Einstein called 'spooky action at a distance.' It ) Tj
T* (transmits no usable signal faster than light, but it is real and now powers quantum computing and quantum cryptography. ) Tj
T* (The wavefunction, once a bookkeeping device, has become engineering.") Tj
