T* (              "content": {) Tj
T* (                "markdown": "Hawking radiation creates a deep paradox. If a black hole evaporates completely, what ) Tj
T* (happens to the information about everything that fell in? Quantum mechanics insists information can't be destroyed; ) Tj
T* (relativity seems to say it's lost. This **black hole information paradox** is one of the sharpest unsolved problems in ) Tj
