T* (              }) Tj
T* (            },) Tj
T* (            {) Tj
T* (              "kind": "DEEPER_DIVE",) Tj
T* (              "title": "Deeper dive: the statistical view",) Tj
T* (              "content": {) Tj
T* (                "markdown": "**Statistical mechanics** derives the gas law and temperature from the behavior of ) Tj
T* ($10^{23}$ particles. Their speeds follow the **Maxwell-Boltzmann distribution**, and temperature is precisely a measure ) Tj
T* (of the spread of that distribution. This bridge -- from the random motion of individual particles to the smooth laws of ) Tj
T* (pressure and temperature -- is one of physics' great unifications, connecting mechanics, probability, and thermodynamics) Tj
T* ( into one framework.") Tj
ET
endstream
