T* (              "content": {) Tj
T* (                "markdown": "Drop a glass and it shatters; you never see shards leap back together. Heat spreads out; it) Tj
T* ( never spontaneously concentrates. This one-way character of nature is the **second law of thermodynamics**, and it is ) Tj
T* (woven from a single quantity: **entropy**.") Tj
T* (              }) Tj
T* (            },) Tj
