T* (              "content": {) Tj
T* (                "markdown": "**Entropy** $S$ measures the disorder of a system -- more precisely, the number of ) Tj
T* (microscopic arrangements consistent with its overall state.\\n\\nThe **second law of thermodynamics:** the total entropy ) Tj
