T* (              "content": {) Tj
T* (                "markdown": "Physicists suspect the four forces are facets of one. At the highest energies of the early ) Tj
T* (universe they may have been unified, splitting apart as the cosmos cooled. The electroweak unification \(Glashow, Salam, ) Tj
T* (Weinberg\) was confirmed when the W and Z bosons were found exactly as predicted. Grand Unified Theories aim to fold in ) Tj
T* (the strong force, and string theory and others seek to include gravity. Success would be the deepest simplification in ) Tj
T* (the history of science -- but nature is guarding the secret well.") Tj
T* (              }) Tj
