T* (                  "Strong force binds nuclei \(gluons\); electromagnetism acts on charge \(photons\).",) Tj
T* (                  "The weak force drives some radioactive decays \(W and Z bosons\).",) Tj
T* (                  "Gravity is weakest but infinite-range and always attractive, so it dominates the cosmos.",) Tj
