T* (              "content": {) Tj
T* (                "markdown": "The **Big Bang** theory: the universe began ~**13.8 billion years ago** in an extremely ) Tj
T* (hot, dense state and has been expanding and cooling ever since. \(It describes the expansion *of* space, not an explosion) Tj
T* ( *into* pre-existing space.\)\\n\\nThree pillars of evidence:\\n\\n1. **Hubble expansion** -- galaxies recede, implying a ) Tj
T* (denser past.\\n2. **The cosmic microwave background \(CMB\)** -- faint microwave radiation filling all the sky, the cooled ) Tj
T* (afterglow of the hot early universe.\\n3. **Primordial abundances** -- the observed ~25% helium \(with hydrogen\) matches ) Tj
T* (Big Bang nucleosynthesis exactly.\\n\\nThe energy budget today is dominated by the **dark sector**:\\n\\n- **~5%** ordinary ) Tj
T* (matter \(everything we see\).\\n- **~27%** **dark matter** -- unseen mass that holds galaxies together \(revealed by ) Tj
T* (rotation curves and lensing\).\\n- **~68%** **dark energy** -- driving accelerating expansion.\\n\\nSo about **95%** of the ) Tj
T* (universe is of unknown composition -- the frontier of physics.") Tj
