T* (                  "Inflation: a burst of exponential expansion in the universe's first instant.",) Tj
T* (                  "It solves the horizon problem \(uniform temperature\) and flatness problem \(flat geometry\).",) Tj
T* (                  "Space can expand faster than light because nothing travels through it.",) Tj
T* (                  "Stretched quantum fluctuations seeded galaxies and clusters.",) Tj
T* (                  "Inflation's predicted ripples match the cosmic microwave background.") Tj
