T* (              "title": "You're standing at the park gates",) Tj
T* (              "content": {) Tj
T* (                "markdown": "Look around the park. Three ducks float on the pond. Five flowers grow by the bench. Two ) Tj
T* (children laugh on the swings.\\n\\nNumbers are how we answer the question **\\"how many?\\"** Counting is one of the very ) Tj
T* (first kinds of math a person ever learns -- and it is everywhere. We count birthday candles, cookies on a plate, steps ) Tj
T* (up to the slide, and friends at the table.\\n\\nToday you'll learn to count carefully and correctly, all the way to ten. ) Tj
T* (Get this right, and every other piece of math you ever meet will stand on top of it.") Tj
T* (              }) Tj
