T* (                "simId": "number-line",) Tj
T* (                "intro": "Set the start number, choose Add, and pick an amount. Take the jumps one at a time -- each hop) Tj
T* ( moves one unit to the right, and the spot you land on is the sum.") Tj
T* (              }) Tj
T* (            },) Tj
T* (            {) Tj
