T* (              "title": "Deeper dive: making ten",) Tj
T* (              "content": {) Tj
T* (                "markdown": "Mathematicians have a favourite trick for adding quickly: **make a ten**. Tens are easy to ) Tj
T* (work with, so we look for pairs that add to 10 -- like $7 + 3$ or $6 + 4$.\\n\\nTo add $8 + 5$, borrow 2 from the 5 to ) Tj
T* (turn the 8 into a 10: $8 + 2 = 10$, with 3 left over, so $10 + 3 = 13$. Spotting \\"friends of ten\\" makes mental ) Tj
T* (addition fast, and it's the same regrouping idea you'll use to add big numbers later on this street.") Tj
T* (              }) Tj
