T* (                  "Addition joins amounts into a total called the sum.",) Tj
T* (                  "The plus sign is $+$; the equals sign means \\"the same amount as\\".",) Tj
T* (                  "Order doesn't matter: $a + b = b + a$.",) Tj
T* (                  "Adding zero leaves a number unchanged.",) Tj
T* (                  "On a number line, adding jumps to the right.") Tj
ET
