T* (                      "Combine: 4 tens and 2 ones.") Tj
T* (                    ],) Tj
T* (                    "answer": "$27 + 15 = 42$.") Tj
T* (                  }) Tj
T* (                ]) Tj
T* (              }) Tj
T* (            },) Tj
