T* (              "kind": "DEEPER_DIVE",) Tj
T* (              "title": "Deeper dive: unit rates are everywhere",) Tj
T* (              "content": {) Tj
T* (                "markdown": "Once you spot them, unit rates run the world. **Fuel economy** is miles per gallon; ) Tj
T* (**typing speed** is words per minute; **heart rate** is beats per minute; a **density** is grams per cubic centimetre; ) Tj
T* (even a **wage** is dollars per hour. Each squeezes a two-number relationship into a single, comparable figure. ) Tj
T* (Supermarkets are even required to print unit prices on shelf tags so shoppers can compare a giant box and a small one ) Tj
T* (fairly -- math protecting your wallet.") Tj
T* (              }) Tj
T* (            },) Tj
T* (            {) Tj
T* (              "kind": "SUMMARY",) Tj
T* (              "title": "Summary",) Tj
T* (              "content": {) Tj
