T* (                  "Always compare to the original \(starting\) value.",) Tj
T* (                  "Discount: pay $\(100 - p\)\\\\%$ of the price; markup adds $p\\\\%$.",) Tj
T* (                  "Successive percent changes use different bases and don't cancel.") Tj
