T* (              "title": "The fountain puzzle",) Tj
T* (              "content": {) Tj
T* (                "markdown": "Carved on the plaza fountain: \\"A number plus 7 equals 12. What is the number?\\" You could ) Tj
T* (guess -- but algebra gives a method that never fails, even when the numbers get ugly. The trick is to think of the ) Tj
T* (equals sign as the pivot of a **balance scale**.") Tj
