T* (                "markdown": "\\"Each extra topping adds \\\\$1.50 to a \\\\$8 pizza.\\" That sentence hides a rule. Written in) Tj
T* ( symbols it's $C = 1.5t + 8$. Drawn on a graph it's a straight line. Real mathematical power comes from translating ) Tj
