T* (              "title": "At the drafting table",) Tj
T* (              "content": {) Tj
T* (                "markdown": "An architect's blueprint is a web of lines meeting at precise angles. Get one angle wrong ) Tj
T* (and walls won't close, roofs won't seal. A handful of simple angle rules let you find every missing measure on a drawing) Tj
T* ( without a protractor.") Tj
