T* (                "markdown": "When a line \(a **transversal**\) crosses two **parallel** lines, it creates matched angle ) Tj
T* (pairs: **corresponding** angles are equal, **alternate interior** angles are equal, and **co-interior** angles are ) Tj
T* (supplementary. These facts are the engine of geometric proof -- they let you transfer an angle from one line to another ) Tj
T* (and conclude, for example, that the three angles of any triangle sum to exactly $180^\\\\circ$.") Tj
