T* (                  "Angles are measured in degrees; acute < 90 < obtuse < 180 = straight.",) Tj
T* (                  "Complementary angles sum to 90 deg.",) Tj
T* (                  "Supplementary angles sum to 180 deg.",) Tj
T* (                  "Angles on a line sum to 180 deg; around a point, 360 deg.",) Tj
