T* (                  "Applies only to right triangles.",) Tj
T* (                  "The hypotenuse $c$ is opposite the right angle and is longest.",) Tj
T* (                  "$a^2 + b^2 = c^2$.",) Tj
T* (                  "Hypotenuse: $c = \\\\sqrt{a^2 + b^2}$; leg: $a = \\\\sqrt{c^2 - b^2}$.",) Tj
T* (                  "The distance formula is this theorem in coordinates.") Tj
T* (                ],) Tj
T* (                "formulas": [) Tj
T* (                  {) Tj
