T* (                    "tex": "P\(1\)\\\\;\\\\wedge\\\\;\\\\big\(P\(k\)\\\\Rightarrow P\(k+1\)\\\\big\)\\\\;\\\\Rightarrow\\\\;\\\\forall n\\\\,P\(n\)") Tj
